text:
Class 6A boys basketball: Top league player of the year candidates for 2016-17   League player of the year candidates in 6A boys basketball 
With the boys basketball regular season coming to a close this week, here's a look at some of the leading candidates for player of the year in the six Class 6A leagues. 
Text by Nick Daschel and JD Humburg; photos by Pete Christopher, Megan Connelly, Kent Frasure, Billy Gates, Serena Morones, Larry Stauth Jr., Carolynn Strode and Kelvin Watkins GENO WEST (PIL)
